radiographic_examinations.findings: Wall thickening and hyperenhancement of the appendiceal base which is dilated to approximately 16 mm with an appendicolith. Significant surrounding inflammatory change with regions of peripheral enhancement measuring approximately 4.0 x 2.7 cm without a large discrete low-density component. No visualized extraluminal/free intraperitoneal air. A small amount of free fluid in the pelvis. A 3.2 x 2.1 cm right adnexal cyst seen.
